quran[12]{c,v,t,f}:
  23,115,"“Ana nkuganichisya ŵanganyammwe kuti Uwwe tun’gumbile wambape (ŵangali masengo gakututendela Uwwe), soni kuti jenumanja Kukwetu ngasim’bujila?”"
  23,116,"Basi atukwiche kusyene Allah, Nchimwene Jwakuonaonape. Pangali nnungu jwine (jwakuŵajilwa kun’galagatila) ikaŵeje Jwelepejo, M’mbuje jwa Arishi Jakuchimbichika kwannope (Chindanda Chaulungu)."
  23,117,"Soni jwatam’bende pampepe ni Allah nnungu jwine, jwanganakola najo umboni (wakuŵajilwa kum’benda), basi nikuti chiŵalanjilo chakwe chili kwa M’mbujegwe. Chisimu makafili nganigaŵa gapundile."
  25,61,"Anyakwiche (pa uchimbichimbi ni upile) Ajula (Allah) jwaŵisile kwinani ndondwa syekulungwa-kulungwa ni mwakwenda mwakwe, ni aŵisile soni kwalakweko nyali (lyuŵa) kwisa soni mwesi wakumulika."
  25,62,"Soni Jwalakwe ni Ajula jwaŵisile chilo ni muusi kuŵa yaakuyaana ni kuchengana-chengana kwa jwaakusaka kumbuchila kapena kusaka kutogolela."
  25,63,"Sano achikapolo ŵa (Allah) Jwaukoto wejinji ni aŵala ŵaakwenda pachilambo mwakulinandiya, nambo soni ajinga ali aŵechete kukwao (maloŵe gangalumbana), akasajangaga ni maloŵe gantima tusya."
  26,34,"(Firiauna) jwasalile achinkulungwa ŵaŵaliji mungulugulu mwakwe kuti: “Chisimu jwalakweju nsaŵi jwakumanyilila nnope (usaŵi).”"
  26,35,"“Jukusaka kuti junkopokasye m’chilambo mwenu ni usaŵi wakweo, ana ni tinnamule yantiuli?”"
  26,36,"Ŵanganyao ŵatite (pakwapanga lunda Afiriauna): “Munnechelesyani panandi jwalakwe ni nkulugwejo (nkaawulaga chitema) ni ntumisye m’misinda akusonganganya.”"
  27,7,"(Kumbuchilani) katema kajwalisalile Musa liŵasa lyakwe kuti: “Chisimu une nauweni moto. Chinam’bichilile najo abali kuumila ku walakweo, kapena chinam’bichilile nacho chisinga chamoto kuti jenumanja n’jote.”"
  27,8,"Basi ndema jajwauŵichilile jwaŵilanjidwe kuti: “Ajaliiwe jwali pamoto ni jwali mungulugulu mwakwe. Nambo soni aswejele Allah M’mbuje jwa iwumbe yosope.”"
  27,9,"“E mmwe Musa! Chisimu Jwalakwejotu ni Une Allah, Jwamachili gakupunda, Jwalunda lwakusokoka.”"